member.param:
If set to , member type 
            must contain  flags;
            otherwise, it must not contain them.

If set to , type 
            must implement ;
            otherwise, it must not implement it.

If set to , method attributes
            must contain  flags;
            otherwise, it must not contain them.

If set to , type
            must have specified method;
            otherwise, it must not have it.
